<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-2')">2</a>. Common with the Chaos Insurgency and several lesser-known organizations with destabilization-oriented goals.</div>
